encuentro (2.1-0ubuntu1) trusty; urgency=medium

  * Bacua parsing improvement.
  * Aesthetic change.
  * No need for explicit unicode strings.
  * Improvements to DQSV episode getting.
  * Tests instructions.
  * Better instructions for the Windows part.
  * Remove redundant logger config.
  * The regex should use bytes when parsing html.
  * Don't log security config (which is now properly stated in a constant)
  * Delayed import of pynotify as much as possible, because of bad interaction
    with PyQt.
  * When update episodes, change the cached normalized title.
  * Update revno in web page.
  * Safe save in all useful ocations.
  * Added the dependency to the LEEME file.
  * Save the column sorting in the correct way.
  * Download and play DQSV content.
  * Final fixes for DQSV metadata.
  * Lot of new cases handling and code for the rest of DQSV.
  * Get images from the SWF.
  * Added more tests for the swf.
  * Scrapping for decimequiensosvos.
  * Use encuentro downloader for encuentro stuff, and auth correctly to
    download better videos.

